- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of a rich narrative representation and character substitution, which are AI techniques. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper may involve training the natural language generation engine. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possibility as the paper may involve retrieving relevant dialogue content from a large database. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses the implementation and evaluation of a potential application for dialogue generation in games.
